com.kontakt.sdk.android.common.model

Interface IManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Manager

    public interface IManager
    Manager represents person using kontakt.io SDK. The manager may belong to Company. The Manager may have one of three roles: OPERATOR, ADMIN, SUPERUSER. Once managers become the owners of beacons, they are the only who is able to manipulate them.
